900
01:36:32,371 --> 01:36:34,289
To je dobro znati.

901
01:36:35,416 --> 01:36:37,501
Negde ce pogrešiti.

902
01:36:37,543 --> 01:36:39,545
I to je dobro znati.

903
01:36:47,386 --> 01:36:48,846
Postoji...

904
01:36:48,846 --> 01:36:51,015
